list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment:
Updated imports using IWYU
Added the optimization flag to the compiler options for ~5 times better performance.

task.summary: Default task
Refactored neighbors to be of type std::vector<std::vector<vertex_t>>
Added AlternatingWalk class
Identified some problems of the implementation
Added signed_distance_t to fix problem with negative gains
Improved visualize.py and optimized Tour::isHamiltonianTour
Optimized VertexList::next
Optimized Tour::isTourAfterExchange
Added ascendingVerticesHeuristic
Added AlWAYS_STORE_IN_MATRIX parameter and optimized AlternatingWalk::containsEdge
Added VertexList::neighborIndex to replace std::find
Fixed g++ warnings

Refactored Tour
Moved VertexList to SimpleHeuristic, added BaseTour and ArrayTour. Tour is now an alias for the subclass of BaseTour that should be used.
Added a greedy algorithm for sorting by signed reversals

Implemented BaseTour::exchange and refactored SignedPermutation
The signed numbers in SignedPermutation are now represented with std::pair<number_t, bool>. BaseTour::exchange might contain errors, the actual reversal is untested.

Fixed errors in BaseTour::exchange and ArrayTour::flip
Also refactored SignedPermutation added comments to SignedPermutation.

Fixed error with double edge in linKernighanHeuristic
Fixed problems in BaseTour::cyclicPermutation, ArrayTour::isBetween and BaseTour::isTourAfterExchange caused by modulo errors (a%b <= 0 if a < 0)
Fixed modulo error in BaseTour::exchange
Fixed all additional modulo errors
Fixed error in BaseTour::exchange
Optimized TsplibProblem::dist

Added the TwoLevelTreeTour class
TwoLevelTreeTour::flip is still unfinished

Refactored TwoLevelTreeTour, so that updating the indices is efficient
TwoLevelTreeTour::flip is not complete
Changed TwoLevelTreeTour::SegmentParent::vertices from vector to list

Implemented TwoLevelTreeTour::flip
but there is a problem with references to SegmentParent inside of SegmentVertex

Change TwoLevelTreeTour::parents' type to std::list
None of the functions in TwoLevelTreeTour was tested!
Fixed a bug in TsplibProblem

Fixed a bug in TsplibProblem::trueDistance
and optimized the Lin-Kernighan-Algorithm to not always recalculate the current gain.
Fixed bug in TwoLevelTreeTour::setVertices
Fixed bug in TwoLevelTreeTour::setVertices
Fixed bug with the implicit copy-constructor of TwoLevelTreeTour
Fixed bug in TwoLevelTreeTour::reverse

Fixed bug in TwoLevelTreeTour::isBetween
The case analysis was not complete. Also added groupSize = 30 for testing purposes (for n <= 1000) and an error if flip is called with illegal arguments.

Fixed a bug in TwoLevelTreeTour::flip
The comparison of sequence numbers needs to respect the reversal bit.

Refactored TwoLevelTreeTour::reverse
TwoLevelTreeTour::reverse has become TwoLevelTreeTour::SegmentParent:: reverseVertices and TwoLevelTreeTour::reverseParents. Also reordered some of the functions of TwoLevelTreeTour and added comments.
Fixed a bug in reverseVertices / reverseParents
Fixed a bug in flip, mergeHalfSegment and isBetween
Fixed a bug in TwoLevelTreeTour for small instances (<= 1000)

Added comments for TwoLevelTreeTour
Also added TODOs and improved visualize.py
Deleted the TourWalker class

Improved LinKernighanHeuristic
Eliminated repeated calls to predecessor(xi) and successor(xi)
Replace assign with resize
Added the CandidateEdges class
Fixed a bug in flip caused by reverseParents
Fixed a bug in flip
Updated date formats
Improved Prim's algorithm and added comments
Improved CandidateEdges::alphaNearestNeighbors
Added the LinKernighanHeuristic class to implement multiple trials
Implemented LinKernighanHeuristic::findBestTour
